# Copy to .env.local and fill in to make the contact form deliver real emails.
# Without this, the form falls back to opening a prefilled mailto: in dev.
#
# Get a FREE access key (no account needed) at https://web3forms.com
#   1. Enter the inbox you want messages delivered to (e.g. wilfridh@prismonex.com)
#   2. They email you an access key
#   3. Paste it below, then restart the dev server
#
# Note: NEXT_PUBLIC_ vars are exposed to the browser. A Web3Forms access key is
# safe to expose by design — it only allows submitting to your chosen inbox.
NEXT_PUBLIC_WEB3FORMS_KEY=
